PR #14, titled "feat(clients): DBUserPersister + harbor-mgmt DATABASE_URL wiring," is open and available at https://github.com/harbor-auth/harbor/pull/14.

Key changes in this PR include:
*   **`internal/clients/users.go`**: Introduction of `DBUserPersister`, which implements the `identity.UserPersister` interface using `db.CreateUser`. It also narrows the `userQuerier` interface and avoids inspecting or logging secrets.
