*   **`cmd/harbor-mgmt/main.go`**: A `connectDB` helper function has been introduced. When `DATABASE_URL` is set, it utilizes the `DBUserPersister`.

The next steps suggested for this PR are to merge it, design a hot-path state strategy, and add an enrollment invariant.

